1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,262
=Episode 11=

17
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,360
Mr. Ye.

18
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,100
You're just in time.

19
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,680
I have a document here
that I'd like Mr. Lu to look at.

20
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:14,880
Mr. Lu isn't in.

21
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,960
Then, do you know when he'll be back?

22
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:19,520
Before Mr. Lu left, he said

23
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:22,290
he had some urgent business today
and wouldn't be returning to the office.

24
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:24,642
Do you know what the urgent business is?

25
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,825
He didn't tell me that.

26
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:30,040
Well, Mr. Ye, I'll get back to work.

27
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,000
Thank you.

28
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,800
Madam.

29
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,120
Man, you're back.

30
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,160
Have you eaten?

31
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,520
I'm not hungry.

32
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,720
Mom, is Lu back yet?

33
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:54,960
Ms. Liu, please heat up the food.

34
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,080
Yes, Madam.

35
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:57,990
Ms. Liu, don't bother. I'm not eating.

36
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,160
Hasn't Mr. Lu come back either?

37
00:02:01,437 --> 00:02:02,677
He's probably working overtime.

38
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,360
I'm not feeling very well today.

39
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,280
I'm going upstairs now.

40
00:02:09,087 --> 00:02:09,862
Mom.

41
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,440
Tell me the truth.

42
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,087
Did something happen to Lu?

43
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:22,720
Yes.

44
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,520
Chen Tianze.

45
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,480
Aren't you Zhu's boyfriend?

46
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:43,500
What do you want with me?

47
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,440
I just want to find
that Hokkien racer from last time

48
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,240
for another race.

49
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,190
Zhu told me
that you're the right person to ask.

50
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,520
You mean Jia?

51
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,090
I haven't seen him in a few days either.

52
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,640
Then, do you know

53
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,240
where he can usually be found?

54
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,280
This guy is either
betting at the race track

55
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,840
or gambling at the pool hall.

56
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:02,840
Why don't you try the pool hall?

57
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,400
I don't know the exact location, though.

58
00:03:15,425 --> 00:03:18,825
(Handsome Cat Metaverse Billiards)

59
00:03:18,887 --> 00:03:19,975
(Joy)

60
00:03:20,037 --> 00:03:23,175
(Sky Billiards)

61
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,360
What are you doing?

62
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,800
I'm sorry.

63
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,710
Where's your boss?

64
00:03:45,725 --> 00:03:46,325
I don't know.

65
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:47,680
Ah.

66
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,360
Where is your boss?

67
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,200
I don't know.

68
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,040
Where is he?

69
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,720
Tell me or not?

70
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,880
I'll take you there.

71
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:21,040
Your dad dared to play tricks on me.

72
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:24,040
If I don't see the money
within six hours,

73
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:27,480
you and this woman will go to heck.

74
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:43,880
Long, I've raced against Jia many times.

75
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,880
Didn't he tell you who I am?

76
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,520
My name is Lu Zhu.

77
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:49,640
How many families
named Lu are there in Hai City?

78
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,920
Call my father.

79
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,360
He will give you the money.

80
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,662
(Business Horizons)

81
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:05,720
I didn't expect
a "buy one, get one free" this time.

82
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:08,840
You're quite loyal.

83
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:10,640
Rushing to sell yourself like this?

84
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:15,440
Why? Is he your man?

85
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,520
My father will be very worried
if he doesn't see me.

86
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:24,080
If it's over 24 hours,
he will call the police.

87
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,920
You'd better hurry up.

88
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,440
Threatening me?

89
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,760
Man.

90
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,240
Another one.

91
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,040
The police will be here in ten minutes.

92
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,120
There's still time to leave now.

93
00:05:53,087 --> 00:05:53,927
Get him!

94
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,400
Man.

95
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,200
Shut up!

96
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,320
Aren't you quite the fighter?

97
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:32,160
If any of you come up, I'll kill him.

98
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,960
Stay back!

99
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,480
What are you doing?

100
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,000
There's one million on this USB key.

101
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,280
Either take it and get lost,

102
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,800
or wait for the police to catch you.

103
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,160
Why should I believe you?

104
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,720
Do you have a choice?

105
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,920
Are you playing with me?

106
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,920
So whatever you say goes?

107
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,220
You can find out for yourself.

108
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,640
Still not leaving?

109
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:23,120
Lu.

110
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,960
I'm sorry.

111
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,850
I'm late.

112
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,520
Man.

113
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:53,000
The private room is inside, let's go.

114
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:53,920
Mom.

115
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,440
There's something I want to ask you.

116
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,360
What is it?

117
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,360
Did you hire someone

118
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,850
to take the photo at home?

119
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,120
What do you mean?

120
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:08,360
I just think
it's too much of a coincidence.

121
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,120
First, Chen Tianze
and Lu Zhu were photographed,

122
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,760
and then they were both kidnapped.

123
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:13,400
So...

124
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,040
Do you know what you're saying?

125
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,160
Are you suspecting
that I had Lu kidnapped?

126
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,160
Man, listen.

127
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:26,000
The girl from the Lu family
is really full of bad ideas.

128
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,000
You've been getting too close to her.

129
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,600
How can you even be affected like this?

130
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:37,440
Ms. Liu brought the photo in
with the newspaper this morning.

131
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,240
But the Lu family
has always been in the spotlight,

132
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,520
and you know that, right?

133
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:43,280
They're eager to spread

134
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,440
more rumors and gossip about our family.

135
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:49,200
They caught Lu with someone else
and thought she was in a relationship.

136
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,240
Maybe they wanted to extort some money.

137
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:53,240
How could you suspect me?

138
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:54,960
It's fine, Mom.

139
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,550
I was overthinking.

140
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:02,880
Man,

141
00:10:03,587 --> 00:10:04,947
you have to trust me.

142
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:06,840
No matter what happens,

143
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,737
I'm the one who loves you most.

144
00:10:10,737 --> 00:10:11,937
I know, Mom.

145
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,440
I'll go order first.

146
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:21,840
(It seems Man has developed
real feelings for that girl.)

147
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,800
(I must speed up the process.)

148
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,520
(I can't let this
continue to worsen gradually.)

149
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,000
(I might as well just go all the way.)

150
00:10:33,425 --> 00:10:37,925
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

151
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:41,938
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

152
00:10:42,113 --> 00:10:46,188
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

153
00:10:46,188 --> 00:10:50,325
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

154
00:10:50,450 --> 00:10:54,225
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

155
00:10:54,225 --> 00:10:58,000
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

156
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,275
♪The you in my memories♪

157
00:11:00,275 --> 00:11:02,288
♪Will fade from clarity♪

158
00:11:02,288 --> 00:11:07,725
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

159
00:11:09,288 --> 00:11:14,725
♪Forget you completely♪
